{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3020_00_01","textHome":"我们家就是所谓的大家族，@我和父亲还有三个妹妹和三个弟弟，@总共八个人一起生活，总之很不容易。@吃饭就和打仗一样，要洗的衣服也和山一样高！@但是，大家在一起都很开心！@所以，我最重要的东西就是“家人”了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"id":302000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302000}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3020_00_18","textHome":"我觉得节约最重要的事是……不要积攒压力。@万事都是如此，不开心的话就无法持续下去！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":302000,"motion":1}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3020_00_19","textHome":"不错不错！就像是积分卡攒满了的感觉！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":200}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3020_00_20","textHome":"感觉不错嘛！@这样的状态，打工的工资也能涨了吧～"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3020_00_21","textHome":"看着拼命工作的父母，自然就想要帮下家里。@就从自己力所能及的事情一点点做起吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":302000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":302000,"motion":400}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3020_00_22","textHome":"说到家务方面的老师，那就是我的母亲了。@光是在一旁边看边模仿学到的各种诀窍……@就足够我钻研一辈子了。@今后我得要把这些都告诉你！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.2,"chara":[{"id":302000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":302000,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":100}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3020_00_23","textHome":"如今是父亲在麻利地干着工作，@家里的事物都由我来处理，@我就是弟弟妹妹们的指挥官！@那么接下来，就开始购物打扫洗衣服……@大家……动起来！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":302000,"motion":100,"pos":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302000,"pos":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":200,"pos":1}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3020_00_24","textHome":"噢，你来啦！欢迎光临！@那么虽然有些突然……@啊，不是去战斗……能否帮我处理一下工作？@拜托了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":200}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3020_00_25","textHome":"早上好！我刚刚送完了报纸。@哎呀～累死了累死了！@接下来就该准备早饭和出门了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":400}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3020_00_26","textHome":"午饭，我平常都是去食堂的。@我拜托了食堂阿姨多给我盛一点。@下午所需的能量，必须好好补充才行！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":1}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3020_00_27","textHome":"这之后的时间表真的很紧……@家里也有很多要忙的事，还要写作业，@还有魔法少女的任务！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":100}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3020_00_03","textHome":"我的家人比什么都重要！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302000}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3020_00_28","textHome":"那么，明天也要早起，也不想浪费电费，@那就赶紧睡吧！睡不着？不要紧！@只要闭上眼睛，说不准什么时候就睡着了哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":100}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3020_00_29","textHome":"送报纸和牛奶的工作学校都是允许的，@但除此之外的工作都是保密的。@也就是所谓秘密的副业哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":100}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3020_00_30","textHome":"虽然每天都把自己当成幸存者来生活，@也总算是走到了现在……@不过，问题还在这之后！@打起精神出发吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":302000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3020_00_31","textHome":"也就是说，要和我自己战斗？@嗯，很有意思嘛！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":302000,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":1}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3020_00_32","textHome":"嚯！这么聚集了这么多人……@诶……总感觉在哪见过这种场景……@啊！是特价大卖场！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":400}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3020_00_33","textHome":"一亿元是完全没法想象的吧。@换句话就是，一块钱的硬币有一亿枚……@啊——不行了，一亿枚也没法想象啊！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":400}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3020_00_34","textHome":"一旦开始节约就会很有趣！@到处寻找便宜的食材，@就像是一场寻找宝物的小冒险一样！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":400}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3020_00_35","textHome":"虽然钱是生存必不可少的东西，@但那更是为了和家人一起生活才需要的。@所以，对我来说最重要的还是家人。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":302000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302000}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3020_00_36","textHome":"有人说钱包里零钱太多会很碍事，但我不信。@我好想把钱包塞到极限啊！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":302000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":400}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3020_00_37","textHome":"别看我这样，我也是家里的长女，@既要照顾弟弟妹妹们，还要陪他们一起玩。@这方面我也会尽力的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.2,"chara":[{"id":302000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":200}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3020_00_04","textHome":"就让你看看，@我在贫困中锻炼出来的毅力！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":100}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3020_00_38","textHome":"魔法少女的战斗确实很残酷。@但正因如此，反而有那种感觉……@就是商机那种啦。@根据？没有根据啦！直觉啦直觉！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":302000,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":0}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3020_00_39","textHome":"天啊……我有预感，我……要有笔大生意了！@太棒了太棒了！@我要大赚一笔了，是人生的一发大逆转！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":200}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3020_00_40","textHome":"成为大财主，我还是不敢想的……@不过，当个小财主应该没问题吧？@对吧！诶？真是没吃够苦头？@啊哈哈，也、也许吧……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302000}]}],